item.description: Updated again! Chris Lyall wonderful world of places Dive into Sydney's electrifying nightclub scene where world-class DJs spin until dawn and the dance floors pulse with energy. From intimate underground venues to rooftop parties with harbor views, discover the hottest spots that define Sydney's after-dark culture.
